issue.message:
`object : BroadcastReceiver() {
        override fun onReceive(context: Context, intent: Intent) {
            context.unregisterReceiver(this)
            val serviceInfo = try {
                intent.getSerializableExtra(EXTRA_SERVICE_INFO) as ServiceInfo
            } catch (e: Exception) {
                it.resumeWithException(e)
                return
            }
            try {
                it.resume(serviceInfo)
            } catch (e: Exception) {
                Log.w(TAG, e)
            }
        }
    }` is missing `RECEIVER_EXPORTED` or `RECEIVER_NOT_EXPORTED` flag for unprotected broadcasts registered for org.microg.gms.gcm.SERVICE_INFO_RESPONSE
